{"id":232914191,"title":"戴佛牌的親身經歷","content":"今天來分享一下我爸爸親身經歷的故事\n\n前情提要 ：我爸爸擔任救護義消20幾年了 在路上遇到車禍都會主動去幫忙\n\n幾年前 我爸爸新請了一面牌 正在欣賞 突然聽到救護車開進我們家的巷子 就順手把牌放在胸口的口袋 就衝去幫忙\n\n很不幸的 是隔壁鄰居OHCA 爸爸就幫忙用長背板將死者搬運下樓\n死者的頭在我爸爸這邊 另一位女消防員負責搬運腳那邊\n\n一下樓 整個重量都壓到我爸爸身上 爸爸只好用腹部頂著 \n\n就在那一霎那 突然有一層光阻隔死者的頭部跟我爸爸的腹部 爸爸腹部的還有一股溫溫熱熱的熱氣在旋轉\n\n好像是冥冥中佛牌在幫忙阻隔一樣\n真的好神奇 \n\n不知道大家有沒有什麼神奇的體驗？\n\n———————————————————\n附上當事佛牌😂\nhttps://i.imgur.com/tKQAcWB.jpg\nhttps://i.imgur.com/gbN4HO2.jpg\n\n———————————————————\n下集預告~\n下集:我們家極陰的正牌","excerpt":"今天來分享一下我爸爸親身經歷的故事，前情提要 ：我爸爸擔任救護義消20幾年了 在路上遇到車禍都會主動去幫忙，幾年前 我爸爸新請了一面牌 正在欣賞 突然聽到救護車開進我們家的巷子 就順手把牌放在胸口的口","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"37a78696-f6a6-48ec-a19f-688f799a2aed","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-18T12:31:12.896Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-18T12:52:27.007Z","commentCount":17,"likeCount":34,"tags":[],"topics":["佛牌","親身經歷"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"靈異","forumAlias":"marvel","school":"國立中興大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":34}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/tKQAcWB.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/gbN4HO2.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"f068bb1c-599b-4fb7-8f75-82e2dc323c91","url":"https://i.imgur.com/tKQAcWBl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/tKQAcWBl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/tKQAcWBl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-18T12:31:12.896Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-18T12:52:27.007Z"},{"id":"f068bb1c-599b-4fb7-8f75-82e2dc323c91","url":"https://i.imgur.com/tKQAcWB.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/tKQAcWB","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/tKQAcWBl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-18T12:31:12.896Z","up